default44default NCVO’s survey of WP subcontractors found that 13 out of 98 have had to ‘park’ customers because the cost of the intervention exceeds the payment. The same research showed that 29 out of 98 respondents believed that prime contractors were inappropriately withholding clients (“creaming”). 
